│ 13825 /// Merges shuffle masks and emits final shuffle instruction, if      │
│ required. It                                                                │
│ 13826 /// supports shuffling of 2 input vectors. It implements lazy         │
│ shuffles emission,                                                          │
│ 13827 /// when the actual shuffle instruction is generated only if this is  │
│ actually                                                                    │
│ 13828 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed  │
│ till the                                                                    │
│ 13829 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions  │
│ and further                                                                 │
│ 13830 /// analysis/transformations.                                         │
│ 13831 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle   │
│ instructions                                                                │
│ 13832 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                       │
│ 13833 /// For example, given the code                                       │
│ 13834 /// \code                                                             │
